headline.print_headline: Online Grocer Peapod Reaches Website Settlement
headline.main: Online Grocer Peapod Reaches Website Settlement

lead_paragraph: Internet grocer Peapod has agreed to make its website more accessible to disabled customers as part of a settlement agreement with the Justice Department.
